    <h1>Scrambled Eggs</h1>
    <p>Eggs are one of my favorate foods. Here is a recipe for deliciously rich scrambled eggs.</p>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
           2 eggs
        </li>
        <li>
           1tbs butter
        </li>
        <li>
           2tbs cream
        </li>
      </ul>
    <h2>Method</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Melt butter in pan over with medium heat.
      </li>
      <li>
        Mix the eggs and cream on the bowl
      </li>
      <li>
        Once butter has melteed add cream and eggs.
      </li>
      <li>
        Using a spatula fold the eggs from the edge of the pan to the center ever 20 seconds.
      </li>
      <li>
        When the eggs are still moist remove from the heat.(It will contrinue to cook on the plate until served.)
      </li>
    </ol>
  </body>
